class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Tool\\AfterToolCallContext"
type: readonly final class
summary: "This readonly final class encapsulates the immutable context required after a tool execution, bundling the assistant's message, the specific tool call, its arguments, and the resulting outcome. It serves as a structured data carrier for propagating tool interaction details within the agent domain."
